  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Diosta kasuspa purishani,
 Palabranmanta willaraspa./
 /Karupis kachun, chiripis kachun,
 Kamachisqanta junfashani./
 
[V2]
 /Tukuy runasman willashani,
 Qanmanpis willallasqaykitaj./
 /Cristo wañorqa, kawsarimorqa.
 Paypi creespa, salvo kanki./
 
[V3]
 /Diospa llajtanman yaykunapaj
 Cristotajap’iy sonqoykipi./
 /Llakiy jamuchun, waqaypis kachun
 Kusiy kawsay cielopi tiyan./
 
</lyrics></song>